{"tid":981142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估國家]瑜珈正妹開高衩露「邪惡視角」 網友暴動：姿勢太讚了！","createTime":"2019-01-14T05:11:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T10:30:52.000Z","uid":46227,"like":302,"dislike":68,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"802d5c380d4cbe098ed522915657d9edc97da4ff","tid":981142,"uid":46227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:11:00.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕近日有網友在PTT表特版分享一系列「正妹練瑜珈」的照片，只見照片中的妹子擺出許多高難度的瑜珈姿勢，讓不少男網友暴動直呼，「瑜珈都穿這種衣服嗎」、「這些姿勢太讚了！」<br />\n<br />\n日在表特板以標題「YOGA的多種姿勢II」PO出多張正妹照片，只見這名瑜珈正妹穿著白色半透明、開高衩的緊身衣，做出一些高難度的瑜珈姿勢，當她在做倒立姿勢時，還因為緊身衣服整個卡在屁股溝中間而露出渾圓的「蜜桃臀」，露出的「蜜大腿」更讓許多網友著迷。<br />\n<br />\n照片曝光後引起網友熱議，紛紛留言，「瑜珈都穿這種衣服嗎」、「蜜大腿」、「最後一張是剛起床的吧」、「這些姿勢太讚了！」、「身材太吸睛，不知道花多少時間在運動」、「真的很棒」，還有網友激動回「啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！」。<br />\n<br />\n有網友用以圖搜圖功能，發現這名瑜珈正妹是南韓人，常常會在IG上分享練瑜珈的照片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpnaPE1I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpnaPE1I.jpg&h=3169371c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瑜珈正妹穿著白色半透明、開高衩緊身衣，做出倒立姿勢時因緊身衣卡進屁股溝中，露出完美的「蜜桃臀」。（翻攝sanga_yogini的IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php49FcLH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php49FcLH.jpg&h=f18d13ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓瑜珈正妹身材相當火辣。（翻攝sanga_yogini的IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpUhjdQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpUhjdQ4.jpg&h=4d1c2192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓瑜珈正妹身材相當火辣。（翻攝sanga_yogini的IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php5rEbKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php5rEbKU.jpg&h=98159dcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓瑜珈正妹身材相當火辣。（翻攝sanga_yogini的IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php5QRr3g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php5QRr3g.jpg&h=db4af1a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓瑜珈正妹身材相當火辣。（翻攝sanga_yogini的IG）"},{"pid":"302964e4537270d9ab4c46fd6ac143bd1116a4d9","tid":981142,"uid":33059,"like":7,"dislike":15,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:11:42.000Z","msg":"又幾正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6ad6d79c9b47483ba522b1db1a0e55d11a19f7","tid":981142,"uid":191812,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3385a2961ab396dcd545188bf0b6830d9c42d78","tid":981142,"uid":46227,"like":4,"dislike":33,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你貼女唔洗推都有人回"},{"pid":"d024761cc9bda3dfad5b1e9b0afabade35635a68","tid":981142,"uid":182499,"like":377,"dislike":36,"score":341,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:15:08.000Z","msg":"泡菜妹泡菜仔先唔講有冇整容，佢地身形真心喺亞洲人種來講最好"},{"pid":"a88ae7dbcae541300511f0359f2fdc4d036b4a72","tid":981142,"uid":46227,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"d024761cc9bda3dfad5b1e9b0afabade35635a68","tid":981142,"uid":182499,"like":377,"dislike":36,"score":341,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:15:08.000Z","msg":"泡菜妹泡菜仔先唔講有冇整容，佢地身形真心喺亞洲人種來講最好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:19:03.000Z","msg":"細細個打跆拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6122673340afd0c8768e1faae8c34e011ea7f6a9","tid":981142,"uid":182499,"like":138,"dislike":1,"score":137,"quote":{"pid":"a88ae7dbcae541300511f0359f2fdc4d036b4a72","tid":981142,"uid":46227,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"d024761cc9bda3dfad5b1e9b0afabade35635a68","tid":981142,"uid":182499,"